------------------------------- DOCUMENTATION ---------------------------------

In order to make get the scripts working, you will need a version of perl with
some basic modules installed. In addition, you will have to make the "modules"
subfolder available to perl e.g. by setting the environment variable PERL5LIB:

% export PERL5LIB="/home/perlstuff/modules"